title: [FSX/P3D] IRIS Pro Training Series Pilatus PC-9/A v1.06.50
description:
This is a CUSTOM installer which I built for you pirates by ripping & updating the recently released IRIS Pro Training Series - Pilatus PC-9/A.

The installer contains both FSX and P3D V2 versions of this aircraft. I also created a small utility so that you can easily switch between the regular interior model and the new performance-oriented interior model which comes with the v1.06.50 update. Refer to the installer's information page for more information.

READ the installer's information page carefully BEFORE installing this package.

SEED and enjoy!
